00:25:42.000 --> 00:25:46.880
over this. Take it as a win.'There

00:25:44.640 --> 00:25:48.880
was a de-escalation of people's hearts

00:25:46.880 --> 00:25:50.880
with the weather and the things

00:25:48.880 --> 00:25:53.679
that manifested. But he goes, 'There's

00:25:50.880 --> 00:25:56.400
certain things that will not be stopped

00:25:53.679 --> 00:25:58.240
through prayer because my word said it

00:25:56.400 --> 00:25:59.600
would come to pass.'As he told us—the

00:25:58.240 --> 00:26:02.240
angel stood right there—he

00:25:59.600 --> 00:26:06.080
said, 'Look at the fig tree. The fig

00:26:02.240 --> 00:26:08.720
tree is ripe. Ezekiel 38 and 39 is at

00:26:06.080 --> 00:26:10.799
the door.

00:26:08.720 --> 00:26:14.000
You don't know where you are in the end

00:26:10.799 --> 00:26:15.679
times, for an acceleration of things

00:26:14.000 --> 00:26:17.840
will take place from the

00:26:15.679 --> 00:26:20.480
seventh month.'I saw the number

00:26:17.840 --> 00:26:23.360
seven; it was on fire.

00:26:20.480 --> 00:26:25.440
And he said, 'An acceleration of war, an

00:26:23.360 --> 00:26:27.120
acceleration of the cleansing of my

00:26:25.440 --> 00:26:30.159
church

00:26:27.120 --> 00:26:33.360
with refiner's fire,

00:26:30.159 --> 00:26:36.880
for I will increase.'1

00:26:33.360 --> 00:26:37.360
Corinthians

00:26:36.880 --> 00:26:40.320
5:5—I

00:26:40.320 --> 00:26:45.678
get

00:26:42.880 --> 00:26:48.880
the numbers mixed up, I apologize—1

00:26:45.679 --> 00:26:52.320
Corinthians 5:5. I will accelerate this

00:26:48.880 --> 00:26:55.679
from the month of July

00:26:52.320 --> 00:26:59.678
to January, and it will start to

00:26:55.679 --> 00:27:02.080
double now, going into 9/11.

00:26:59.679 --> 00:27:07.799
An acceleration of events will start

00:27:02.080 --> 00:27:07.799
to take place. He warned me: war,

00:27:08.080 --> 00:27:12.399
an acceleration.

00:27:10.000 --> 00:27:14.640
You'll hear of wars and rumors of wars—acceleration.

00:27:12.400 --> 00:27:17.279
I think even whenever

00:27:14.640 --> 00:27:20.400
I told Joel Renner—Rick Renner's son, Rick Renner—he

00:27:17.279 --> 00:27:21.919
came

00:27:20.400 --> 00:27:24.240
to our church for a while and asked,

00:27:21.919 --> 00:27:26.000
'So what's coming?'Sometimes

00:27:24.240 --> 00:27:27.600
when you say things to

00:27:26.000 --> 00:27:29.200
people, they look at you

00:27:27.600 --> 00:27:32.399
like a cow at a new gate—you know,

00:27:29.200 --> 00:27:33.760
a cow chewing its cud.

00:27:32.400 --> 00:27:35.039
They look at you like, 'Okay,

00:27:33.760 --> 00:27:37.200
we'll see what happens.'I say, 'Watch

00:27:35.039 --> 00:27:38.799
Poland. Watch.'I'm not criticizing

00:27:37.200 --> 00:27:40.640
him because I don't know him very well,

00:27:38.799 --> 00:27:42.960
but people ask. I'm just telling you

00:27:40.640 --> 00:27:45.360
what I see. This is what the Lord shows

00:27:42.960 --> 00:27:47.440
me. They're always curious. This

00:27:45.360 --> 00:27:51.360
is what the Lord is showing me:

00:27:47.440 --> 00:27:54.720
watch Poland; watch all these

00:27:51.360 --> 00:27:56.959
different areas. I saw

00:27:54.720 --> 00:27:59.600
war, an acceleration of

00:27:56.960 --> 00:28:01.360
World War III. This was

00:27:59.600 --> 00:28:04.480
about a year or two ago,

00:28:04.480 --> 00:28:10.399
before Rick came to church. I am

00:28:08.159 --> 00:28:11.520
looking into it.

00:28:10.399 --> 00:28:12.719
Whenever you're seeing in a

00:28:11.520 --> 00:28:14.480
vision, sometimes it looks like it's right

00:28:12.720 --> 00:28:16.399
in front of your face, like it's going

00:28:14.480 --> 00:28:18.399
to happen tomorrow, but

00:28:16.399 --> 00:28:20.239
there is

00:28:18.399 --> 00:28:22.479
a process of time. That's

00:28:20.240 --> 00:28:25.919
what I'm learning. It's very hard to

00:28:22.480 --> 00:28:28.480
pinpoint time in visions because

00:28:25.919 --> 00:28:30.720
God is infinite.

00:28:28.480 --> 00:28:32.000
When you're looking in a

00:28:30.720 --> 00:28:33.679
vision, it looks like it's right in front

00:28:32.000 --> 00:28:34.880
of your face, but sometimes that 'right in

00:28:33.679 --> 00:28:37.520
front of your face'is two

00:28:34.880 --> 00:28:40.159
to three years, and

00:28:37.520 --> 00:28:41.600
sometimes it's tomorrow.

00:28:40.159 --> 00:28:42.480
Like when I'm seeing churches burning, I'm

00:28:41.600 --> 00:28:44.480
thinking that's going to happen

00:28:42.480 --> 00:28:46.640
later on, but it's happening right now.

00:28:44.480 --> 00:28:48.720
Churches are burning and the Lord said

00:28:46.640 --> 00:28:50.480
it.

00:28:48.720 --> 00:28:53.440
I don't try to pinpoint

00:28:50.480 --> 00:28:55.360
time; I see in part and I hear in part. I

00:28:53.440 --> 00:28:56.559
don't want to get flaky with it because

00:28:55.360 --> 00:28:57.760
there's a lot of flakiness in the

00:28:56.559 --> 00:29:00.158
prophetic, and I think it's because

00:28:57.760 --> 00:29:01.520
people just don't understand it. Daniel

00:29:00.159 --> 00:29:03.600
saw things happening in the

00:29:01.520 --> 00:29:05.120
Tribulation that still haven't

00:29:03.600 --> 00:29:07.279
come to pass thousands of

00:29:05.120 --> 00:29:09.520
years later.

00:29:07.279 --> 00:29:10.799
Daniel said, 'I see this,'and I'm sure he was

00:29:09.520 --> 00:29:13.918
thinking it was

00:29:10.799 --> 00:29:15.279
about to happen, but thousands of years later,

00:29:15.279 --> 00:29:19.919
it

00:29:18.000 --> 00:29:21.919
still hasn't manifested. People might say

00:29:19.919 --> 00:29:24.000
he's a false prophet, but he's in

00:29:21.919 --> 00:29:26.399
the Bible.

00:29:26.399 --> 00:29:29.840
When

00:29:28.320 --> 00:29:31.918
you're looking in the spirit, you think

00:29:29.840 --> 00:29:34.000
it's tomorrow, but it's years. Now Poland

00:29:31.919 --> 00:29:36.000
is happening. I

00:29:34.000 --> 00:29:39.120
remember going on Kim Clement's Donne's

00:29:36.000 --> 00:29:42.799
Channel and I warned about this over a

00:29:39.120 --> 00:29:45.520
year ago on July 11th.

00:29:42.799 --> 00:29:47.440
I told

00:29:45.520 --> 00:29:49.520
y'all what the Lord showed me about this

00:29:47.440 --> 00:29:52.480
and she said, 'I remember Daddy having a

00:29:49.520 --> 00:29:54.639
vision about

00:29:52.480 --> 00:29:58.000
Poland and that area.'She said God sent her father to Poland, and she

00:29:58.000 --> 00:30:01.520
went there to

00:29:59.840 --> 00:30:04.399
the

00:30:01.520 --> 00:30:07.760
woods. I said I didn't see the woods;

00:30:04.399 --> 00:30:11.279
I saw buildings burning and a major

00:30:07.760 --> 00:30:13.840
mushroom cloud;

00:30:11.279 --> 00:30:15.360
it was an acceleration. Going

00:30:13.840 --> 00:30:18.480
back to all of this:

00:30:15.360 --> 00:30:19.918
I saw that young man and

00:30:18.480 --> 00:30:21.360
the youth building, and that's

00:30:19.919 --> 00:30:23.440
why it's been on my heart to build it so fast. The Lord put it on me to pray over that

00:30:21.360 --> 00:30:25.439
youth building.

00:30:27.039 --> 00:30:30.640
The city held it up for so long;

00:30:29.200 --> 00:30:31.760
they didn't want it built.

00:30:31.760 --> 00:30:36.320
This is the Red Zone. You see

00:30:33.679 --> 00:30:37.600
that gap from that

00:30:36.320 --> 00:30:38.960
building to that building? That's where

00:30:37.600 --> 00:30:40.559
we're building the new youth building;

00:30:38.960 --> 00:30:42.320
the structure is being

00:30:40.559 --> 00:30:44.799
built right now. I

00:30:42.320 --> 00:30:46.639
just have to make sure...

00:30:52.159 --> 00:30:53.760
I'm showing it right now.

00:30:54.880 --> 00:30:59.600
From there to

00:30:56.960 --> 00:31:03.440
there is where we're building it

00:30:59.600 --> 00:31:06.158
right now. That

00:31:03.440 --> 00:31:08.880
is what the city blocked us for over the

00:31:06.159 --> 00:31:10.480
last year. Finally, we got the

00:31:08.880 --> 00:31:12.399
permit. I was so excited because

00:31:10.480 --> 00:31:15.600
we've been praying over this.

00:31:12.399 --> 00:31:18.399
This is the Red Zone, Champions for

00:31:15.600 --> 00:31:20.000
Christ. This is where I see this boy

00:31:18.399 --> 00:31:21.120
coming in across the

00:31:20.000 --> 00:31:22.880
street from the football stadium.

00:31:22.880 --> 00:31:28.480
As the church is

00:31:26.000 --> 00:31:30.000
going on, we have tables out

00:31:28.480 --> 00:31:32.000
here giving

00:31:30.000 --> 00:31:34.000
him pizza and Cokes

00:31:32.000 --> 00:31:35.919
to get them

00:31:34.000 --> 00:31:37.840
excited. They're making a big garage

00:31:35.919 --> 00:31:39.600
with a game room for

00:31:37.840 --> 00:31:41.678
them to come over after the game for

00:31:39.600 --> 00:31:43.678
an afterparty.

00:31:41.679 --> 00:31:45.600
We call it the

00:31:43.679 --> 00:31:46.880
Red Zone. This has

00:31:45.600 --> 00:31:48.480
been my heart.

00:31:46.880 --> 00:31:50.000
I've been

00:31:48.480 --> 00:31:53.120
interceding for this building because

00:31:50.000 --> 00:31:55.679
the Lord said the young man will be used, he

00:31:53.120 --> 00:31:58.799
will be put in a school, and

00:31:55.679 --> 00:32:00.880
revival will come from this boy. He

00:31:58.799 --> 00:32:03.600
will save lots of college kids because

00:32:00.880 --> 00:32:04.799
he will be like a David to me.

00:32:04.799 --> 00:32:07.840
The city blocked

00:32:06.880 --> 00:32:10.000
it and said, 'We're not going to let

00:32:07.840 --> 00:32:12.879
you build it.'I

00:32:10.000 --> 00:32:14.640
said, 'You will;

00:32:12.880 --> 00:32:16.880
this is discrimination.'They finally

00:32:14.640 --> 00:32:19.679
let it go. We had 14 people pray and

00:32:16.880 --> 00:32:23.440
they broke that

00:32:19.679 --> 00:32:24.799
through.

00:32:23.440 --> 00:32:26.399
It's

00:32:24.799 --> 00:32:28.960
being built right there in that

00:32:26.399 --> 00:32:31.678
field.

00:32:28.960 --> 00:32:33.760
It's exciting what God is doing in

00:32:31.679 --> 00:32:35.519
these last days. That

00:32:33.760 --> 00:32:38.000
field is going to be

00:32:35.519 --> 00:32:41.360
the new building. The

00:32:38.000 --> 00:32:41.760
high school stadium is

00:32:43.279 --> 00:32:47.440
where the

00:32:44.320 --> 00:32:49.918
Collinsville Cardinals play.

00:32:51.840 --> 00:32:56.879
They walk across the

00:32:54.080 --> 00:32:58.639
street and go to the party. That is what

00:32:56.880 --> 00:33:00.480
my vision is.

00:33:01.679 --> 00:33:05.760
I saw that young man being drafted to

00:33:03.279 --> 00:33:08.320
war one day and the Lord said, 'You have

00:33:05.760 --> 00:33:10.240
a window;

00:33:08.320 --> 00:33:13.279
things are going to escalate.'You ask,

00:33:10.240 --> 00:33:16.399
'Can we stop war?'No, you can't stop

00:33:13.279 --> 00:33:20.640
war because of wars and rumors of wars in

00:33:16.399 --> 00:33:22.158
Matthew 24. I

00:33:20.640 --> 00:33:23.519
believe with all my heart we are in the

00:33:22.159 --> 00:33:25.039
last of the last days.

00:33:25.039 --> 00:33:29.279
There'll be things that happen.

00:33:27.200 --> 00:33:31.279
We

00:33:29.279 --> 00:33:33.519
can delay it sometimes, but we will

00:33:31.279 --> 00:33:36.320
ultimately see the end come

00:33:33.519 --> 00:33:37.840
because Jesus said it would.

00:33:36.320 --> 00:33:39.279
We're going to see

00:33:37.840 --> 00:33:41.600
plagues and pestilence;

00:33:41.600 --> 00:33:47.039
this is the beginning of sorrows. People

00:33:44.399 --> 00:33:49.439
go, 'Well, Brandon, the Tribulation's

00:33:47.039 --> 00:33:53.279
not going to be too bad.'It's

00:33:49.440 --> 00:33:56.080
going to be hell on earth.

00:33:56.080 --> 00:34:01.439
You've never seen anything like this. Think of

00:33:59.600 --> 00:34:03.360
when the Romans

00:34:01.440 --> 00:34:06.240
tortured Christians in the

00:34:03.360 --> 00:34:08.239
Coliseum

00:34:06.240 --> 00:34:10.000
and they would send the lions out for

00:34:08.239 --> 00:34:11.678
sport.

00:34:13.839 --> 00:34:17.040
They would cheer

00:34:15.040 --> 00:34:19.759
as they watched

00:34:17.040 --> 00:34:22.320
Christians be crucified.

00:34:22.320 --> 00:34:27.839
That's a sick culture.

00:34:31.760 --> 00:34:38.079
But we are entering into a time of

00:34:35.359 --> 00:34:42.239
godlessness.

00:34:42.239 --> 00:34:45.439
The prayer covering will go.

00:34:45.440 --> 00:34:49.760
I believe in the rapture of the church.

00:34:47.280 --> 00:34:53.440
When the remnant

00:34:49.760 --> 00:34:56.159
are taken out, that

00:34:53.440 --> 00:34:58.240
restraining force called the Church is gone.

00:35:03.440 --> 00:35:07.599
You're about to see a shaking like

00:35:05.920 --> 00:35:08.880
you've never seen before.

00:35:07.599 --> 00:35:10.880
People say, 'I believe there's

00:35:08.880 --> 00:35:12.480
going to be revival in the

00:35:10.880 --> 00:35:14.480
Tribulation.'I'm

00:35:14.480 --> 00:35:18.240
not doubting that people will give their hearts

00:35:16.079 --> 00:35:20.880
to Jesus Christ, but it's

00:35:25.599 --> 00:35:30.480
about finishing the race.

00:35:27.680 --> 00:35:34.240
Everybody can start, but it's

00:35:30.480 --> 00:35:36.240
about finishing.

00:35:34.240 --> 00:35:39.118
There'll be many people who start who

00:35:36.240 --> 00:35:40.959
will not finish.

00:35:39.119 --> 00:35:44.160
I don't care what you say with your

00:35:40.960 --> 00:35:45.920
mouth; it's about finishing. Someone might

00:35:44.160 --> 00:35:49.759
say, 'Well, Brandon,

00:35:45.920 --> 00:35:52.640
I was all in for a day.'It's

00:35:49.760 --> 00:35:55.280
about finishing the race. I saw

00:35:52.640 --> 00:35:56.879
people in the Tribulation

00:35:55.280 --> 00:35:58.800
who

00:35:56.880 --> 00:36:00.560
were disappointed and mad at the

00:35:58.800 --> 00:36:03.040
Lord because they did not have their

00:36:00.560 --> 00:36:06.400
lamps full of oil and they were left

00:36:03.040 --> 00:36:10.480
behind. They believed in a false grace

00:36:06.400 --> 00:36:12.000
gospel that was just a soupy grace. We

00:36:10.480 --> 00:36:13.440
can live the way we want to live. They

00:36:12.000 --> 00:36:14.800
live like a bunch of alley cats, sleeping

00:36:13.440 --> 00:36:16.240
around, doing everything, going to

00:36:14.800 --> 00:36:18.079
strip clubs, and doing things,

00:36:16.240 --> 00:36:20.640
thinking, "Well, we're saved, brother,

00:36:18.079 --> 00:36:22.400
because it's under grace,"but they live

00:36:20.640 --> 00:36:24.078
like hell

00:36:22.400 --> 00:36:28.720
and didn't think they had to

00:36:24.079 --> 00:36:30.800
live a pure life. I saw them left

00:36:28.720 --> 00:36:32.160
and flipping off the Lord.

00:36:30.800 --> 00:36:33.760
They were giving him the finger. They

00:36:32.160 --> 00:36:35.598
were cursing him. They were mad because

00:36:33.760 --> 00:36:38.000
they were left. Then they were

00:36:35.599 --> 00:36:40.560
looking for the preachers who preached a

00:36:38.000 --> 00:36:43.200
lukewarm gospel to them, and they hung

00:36:40.560 --> 00:36:47.599
them right there in the streets;

00:36:43.200 --> 00:36:51.439
they strung them up.

00:36:47.599 --> 00:36:53.680
They were mad. They were angry. They

00:36:51.440 --> 00:36:56.079
would say, "You preached us a false gospel."I

00:36:53.680 --> 00:36:57.919
saw people on TV—TBN,

00:36:56.079 --> 00:37:00.960
Daystar,

00:36:57.920 --> 00:37:02.960
and some of these

00:37:00.960 --> 00:37:04.800
TV networks that were on there on a

00:37:02.960 --> 00:37:07.040
regular basis preaching the gospel—who

00:37:04.800 --> 00:37:08.880
were left behind.

00:37:07.040 --> 00:37:11.839
They were looking for them and

00:37:08.880 --> 00:37:14.240
killed them. I'm telling you

00:37:11.839 --> 00:37:16.799
the truth. I was there with Jesus and I

00:37:14.240 --> 00:37:19.839
saw them murder those

00:37:16.800 --> 00:37:22.000
preachers because they did not preach

00:37:19.839 --> 00:37:24.720
the truth, and they were mad they were

00:37:22.000 --> 00:37:26.800
left.

00:37:24.720 --> 00:37:28.480
A lot of them joined up and created

00:37:26.800 --> 00:37:31.359
communities.

00:37:28.480 --> 00:37:33.839
They went to the hills,

00:37:31.359 --> 00:37:36.560
the Ozarks,

00:37:33.839 --> 00:37:40.000
the Rockies, and

00:37:36.560 --> 00:37:43.119
the Smoky Mountains, and they had

00:37:40.000 --> 00:37:44.880
camps or colonies of people.

00:37:43.119 --> 00:37:46.160
They tried to join together and

00:37:44.880 --> 00:37:49.119
brought

00:37:46.160 --> 00:37:54.160
their supplies, but the weather

00:37:49.119 --> 00:37:57.040
was crazy and it was the coldest winters

00:37:54.160 --> 00:37:59.440
you can ever imagine. They could not

00:37:57.040 --> 00:38:02.720
burn fires

00:37:59.440 --> 00:38:04.880
because the

00:38:02.720 --> 00:38:06.959
military drones would see them and

00:38:04.880 --> 00:38:09.200
tell on you. If they

00:38:06.960 --> 00:38:11.599
saw smoke, heat, or anything through

00:38:09.200 --> 00:38:15.279
infrared,

00:38:15.280 --> 00:38:22.160
they would

00:38:18.320 --> 00:38:25.359
send the troops out to get you.

00:38:22.160 --> 00:38:26.960
You couldn't stay warm.

00:38:25.359 --> 00:38:28.560
In the summer, you could keep

00:38:26.960 --> 00:38:32.079
cool by dipping in the water if you got

00:38:28.560 --> 00:38:34.160
too hot, but the winter was bad.

00:38:32.079 --> 00:38:36.640
I saw the people running and trying

00:38:34.160 --> 00:38:39.598
to hide, trying to stay alive. There was

00:38:36.640 --> 00:38:42.160
no food and no clean

00:38:39.599 --> 00:38:44.000
water. There was a pestilence upon the

00:38:42.160 --> 00:38:47.440
land. As you drank the water, it

00:38:44.000 --> 00:38:49.680
made you sick, and you had diarrhea and

00:38:47.440 --> 00:38:51.920
vomiting because people's systems are

00:38:49.680 --> 00:38:54.480
used to purified water. We don't know

00:38:51.920 --> 00:38:56.640
what it's like to have dirty water and

00:38:54.480 --> 00:38:59.200
drink it out of a ditch like some of our

00:38:56.640 --> 00:39:00.720
ancestors did.

00:38:59.200 --> 00:39:02.240
They would drink things and boil them

00:39:00.720 --> 00:39:04.160
to stay alive, but people

00:39:02.240 --> 00:39:06.879
don't know how to do that now. They're

00:39:04.160 --> 00:39:08.799
all domesticated. They know how to go to

00:39:06.880 --> 00:39:11.680
the faucet and turn it on.

00:39:08.800 --> 00:39:13.760
But if you ask, "How do

